name: ONIMATA-12
description:
AKUMU SERIES

Set of 4
4 of 4

AKUMU is a group of extraordinary ONIMATA with a mission to search for a LUDEN. TEIKO is one of their target because TEIKO have something they always wanted, a scroll with a map to the FORBIDDEN LAB in it.

---------------

ONIMATA PROJECT (オニマタ) is my visual storytelling project that felling stories about a group of demons who survived the post apocalyptic world which caused by the unknown organization.

ONI means demon in Japanese, and MATA means eye in Bahasa Indonesia.
